data.meta_description:
172 likes, 1 comments - goetheinstitut_newdelhi on April 21, 2024: "2024 marks the 300th birthday of the philosopher, Immanuel Kant, born in Königsberg in 1724. His work remains foundational in Enlightenment philosophy, inspiring generations with his emphasis on reason and human dignity. 

In this special edition, we explore his lessons, failures, and complexities and witness how Kant’s philosophy has influenced individuals and the society. 

Find out more at goethe.de/india/kant (link in bio).
 
#kant #300yearskant #immanuelkant #300jahrekant #maxmuellerbhavannewdelhi♥ #goetheinstitut".
